  "type": "Collection",
  "id": "sentinel-1-sar-opendr",
  "title": "OpenDR 1.0 Sentinel-1 SAR Inundation Collection",
  "description": "Multi-sensor C-band Synthetic Aperture Radar (SAR) collection optimized for real-time flood assessment in transboundary basins. Data is provided in FLOAT power scale to support Adaptive Otsu Thresholding microservices as per Markert et al. (2024).",
  "keywords": [
    "SAR",
    "Sentinel-1",
    "Flood Inundation",
    "Cloud-Native",
    "OpenDR",
    "East Africa"
  ],
